step.reason:
\begin{align}
  \log \sin x =t &\implies \dfrac{1}{\sin x} \cdot \cos x \cdot \dfrac{dx}{dt}=1\\
                    &\implies  \dfrac{1}{\sin x} \cdot \cos x \cdot dx= dt
\end{align}

